01:08:46,207 --> 01:08:50,211
<font color="#FFFFFF">But my island is dying...</font>

988
01:08:51,045 --> 01:08:54,047
<font color="#FFFFFF">so I am here.</font>

989
01:08:54,715 --> 01:08:57,091
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's just me and you.</font>

990
01:08:57,259 --> 01:08:59,929
<font color="#FFFFFF">And I want to help...</font>

991
01:09:00,095 --> 01:09:04,390
<font color="#FFFFFF">but I can't if you don't let me.</font>

992
01:09:09,771 --> 01:09:12,315
<font color="#FFFFFF">I wasn't born a demigod.</font>

993
01:09:12,983 --> 01:09:15,109
<font color="#FFFFFF">I had human parents.</font>

994
01:09:17,488 --> 01:09:21,449
<font color="#FFFFFF">They took one look and decided...</font>

995
01:09:21,617 --> 01:09:24,078
<font color="#FFFFFF">they did not want me.</font>

996
01:09:24,411 --> 01:09:26,538
<font color="#FFFFFF">They threw me into the sea...</font>

997
01:09:26,997 --> 01:09:30,125
<font color="#FFFFFF">like I was nothing.</font>

998
01:09:31,668 --> 01:09:35,130
<font color="#FFFFFF">Somehow, I was found by the gods.</font>

999
01:09:35,296 --> 01:09:36,923
<font color="#FFFFFF">They gave me the hook.</font>

1000
01:09:37,591 --> 01:09:38,759
<font color="#FFFFFF">They made me...</font>

1001
01:09:39,592 --> 01:09:40,594
<font color="#FFFFFF">Maui.</font>

1002
01:09:41,970 --> 01:09:44,640
<font color="#FFFFFF">And back to the humans I went.</font>

1003
01:09:45,099 --> 01:09:48,978
<font color="#FFFFFF">I gave them islands, fire, coconuts.</font>

1004
01:09:49,979 --> 01:09:52,273
<font color="#FFFFFF">Anything they could ever want.</font>

1005
01:09:52,981 --> 01:09:55,275
<font color="#FFFFFF">You took the heart for them.</font>

1006
01:09:55,984 --> 01:09:58,863
<font color="#FFFFFF">You did everything for them.</font>

1007
01:09:59,697 --> 01:10:01,532
<font color="#FFFFFF">So they'd love you.</font>

1008
01:10:02,115 --> 01:10:05,286
<font color="#FFFFFF">It was never enough.</font>

1009
01:10:13,377 --> 01:10:16,713
<font color="#FFFFFF">Maybe the gods found you for a reason.</font>

1010
01:10:16,881 --> 01:10:20,050
<font color="#FFFFFF">Maybe the ocean brought you to them...</font>

1011
01:10:20,216 --> 01:10:24,305
<font color="#FFFFFF">because it saw someone
who was worthy of being saved.</font>

1012
01:10:25,555 --> 01:10:29,143
<font color="#FFFFFF">But the gods aren't the ones
who make you Maui.</font>

1013
01:10:29,851 --> 01:10:31,060
<font color="#FFFFFF">You are.</font>

1014
01:10:40,529 --> 01:10:42,363
<font color="#FFFFFF">Okay, okay.</font>

1015
01:10:43,323 --> 01:10:45,826
<font color="#FFFFFF">I love you, too, buddy.</font>

1016
01:11:51,809 --> 01:11:52,810
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah!</font>

1017
01:12:17,001 --> 01:12:19,627
<font color="#FFFFFF">Next stop, Te Fiti.</font>

1018
01:13:06,466 --> 01:13:07,467
<font color="#FFFFFF">What?</font>

1019
01:13:07,634 --> 01:13:09,136
<font color="#FFFFFF">I figured it out.</font>

1020
01:13:10,470 --> 01:13:14,182
<font color="#FFFFFF">You know, the ocean used to love
when I pulled up islands...</font>

1021
01:13:14,349 --> 01:13:18,145
<font color="#FFFFFF">'cause your ancestors
would sail her seas and find 'em.</font>

1022
01:13:18,811 --> 01:13:21,774
<font color="#FFFFFF">All those new lands, new villages.</font>

1023
01:13:22,149 --> 01:13:24,609
<font color="#FFFFFF">It was the water that connected 'em all.</font>

1024
01:13:24,984 --> 01:13:26,653
<font color="#FFFFFF">And if I were the ocean...</font>

1025
01:13:26,819 --> 01:13:30,908
<font color="#FFFFFF">I think I'd be looking for
a curly-haired non-princess...</font>

1026
01:13:31,658 --> 01:13:33,493
<font color="#FFFFFF">to start that again.</font>

1027
01:13:33,659 --> 01:13:38,039
<font color="#FFFFFF">That is literally the nicest thing
you've ever said to me.</font>

1028
01:13:39,082 --> 01:13:41,210
<font color="#FFFFFF">Probably should have saved it
for Te Fiti.</font>

1029
01:13:42,836 --> 01:13:43,921
<font color="#FFFFFF">I did.</font>

1030
01:13:46,756 --> 01:13:48,926
<font color="#FFFFFF">Moana of Motunui...</font>

1031
01:13:49,259 --> 01:13:54,722
<font color="#FFFFFF">I believe you have officially
delivered Maui across the great sea.</font>

1032
01:13:55,849 --> 01:13:58,351
<font color="#FFFFFF">Moana! Moana! Moana!</font>

1033
01:13:58,810 --> 01:14:00,604
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're so amazing!</font>

1034
01:14:02,396 --> 01:14:03,398
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's time.</font>

1035
01:14:21,707 --> 01:14:23,252
<font color="#FFFFFF">Go save the world.</font>

1036
01:14:46,984 --> 01:14:48,694
<font color="#FFFFFF">Maui!</font>

1037
01:15:22,644 --> 01:15:23,895
<font color="#FFFFFF">What are you doing?</font>

1038
01:15:24,145 --> 01:15:25,814
<font color="#FFFFFF">Finding you a better way in!</font>

1039
01:15:27,481 --> 01:15:29,193
<font color="#FFFFFF">- We won't make it!
- Yes, we will!</font>

1040
01:15:29,359 --> 01:15:30,484
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Turn around!
- No!</font>

1041
01:15:30,652 --> 01:15:31,778
<font color="#FFFFFF">Moana, stop!</font>

1042
01:15:31,944 --> 01:15:32,945
<font color="#FFFFFF">No!</font>

1043
01:16:00,890 --> 01:16:02,643
<font color="#FFFFFF">Are you okay?</font>

1044
01:16:04,185 --> 01:16:05,186
<font color="#FFFFFF">Maui?</font>

1045
01:16:13,028 --> 01:16:14,947
<font color="#FFFFFF">I told you to turn back.</font>

1046
01:16:17,240 --> 01:16:18,992
<font color="#FFFFFF">I thought we could make it.</font>

1047
01:16:19,326 --> 01:16:20,409
<font color="#FFFFFF">We?</font>

1048
01:16:21,869 --> 01:16:23,956
<font color="#FFFFFF">I thought I could make it.</font>

1049
01:16:25,832 --> 01:16:27,042
<font color="#FFFFFF">We can fix it.</font>

1050
01:16:27,208 --> 01:16:29,336
<font color="#FFFFFF">It was made by the gods.</font>

1051
01:16:29,502 --> 01:16:31,255
<font color="#FFFFFF">You can't fix it!</font>

1052
01:16:31,546 --> 01:16:33,756
<font color="#FFFFFF">Next time we'll be more careful.</font>

1053
01:16:34,048 --> 01:16:36,092
<font color="#FFFFFF">Te Kā was stuck on the barrier islands.</font>

1054
01:16:36,260 --> 01:16:38,679
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's lava, it can't go in the water.</font>

1055
01:16:38,845 --> 01:16:40,846
<font color="#FFFFFF">We can find a way around.</font>

1056
01:16:41,014 --> 01:16:42,849
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm not going back.</font>

1057
01:16:44,016 --> 01:16:45,560
<font color="#FFFFFF">We still have to restore the heart.</font>

1058
01:16:45,851 --> 01:16:47,229
<font color="#FFFFFF">My hook is cracked.</font>

1059
01:16:47,395 --> 01:16:49,064
<font color="#FFFFFF">One more hit, and it's over.</font>

1060
01:16:49,439 --> 01:16:51,315
<font color="#FFFFFF">Maui, you have to restore the heart.</font>

1061
01:16:51,649 --> 01:16:53,359
<font color="#FFFFFF">Without my hook, I am nothing.</font>

1062
01:16:53,527 --> 01:16:54,694
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's not true!</font>

1063
01:16:54,860 --> 01:16:57,363
<font color="#FFFFFF">Without my hook, I am nothing!</font>

1064
01:17:06,914 --> 01:17:08,166
<font color="#FFFFFF">We are only here...</font>

1065
01:17:08,542 --> 01:17:11,461
<font color="#FFFFFF">because you stole the heart
in the first place.</font>

1066
01:17:12,753 --> 01:17:15,381
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, we're here because
the ocean told you you're special...</font>

1067
01:17:15,548 --> 01:17:17,341
<font color="#FFFFFF">and you believed it.</font>

1068
01:17:18,592 --> 01:17:21,095
<font color="#FFFFFF">I am Moana of Motunui.</font>

1069
01:17:21,262 --> 01:17:23,472
<font color="#FFFFFF">- You will board my boat...
- Goodbye, Moana.</font>

1070
01:17:23,640 --> 01:17:24,807
<font color="#FFFFFF">sail across the sea...</font>

1071
01:17:24,975 --> 01:17:26,059
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm not killing myself...</font>

1072
01:17:26,225 --> 01:17:27,476
<font color="#FFFFFF">so you can prove
you're something you're not!</font>

1073
01:17:27,644 --> 01:17:28,895
<font color="#FFFFFF">and restore the heart of Te Fiti!</font>

1074
01:17:29,604 --> 01:17:31,981
<font color="#FFFFFF">The ocean chose me!</font>

1075
01:17:32,940 --> 01:17:34,650
<font color="#FFFFFF">It chose wrong.</font>

1076
01:17:44,368 --> 01:17:45,453
<font color="#FFFFFF">Maui!</font>

1077
01:18:00,426 --> 01:18:02,929
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why did you bring me here?</font>

1078
01:18:07,768 --> 01:18:09,770
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm not the right person.</font>

1079
01:18:12,605 --> 01:18:15,442
<font color="#FFFFFF">You have to choose someone else.</font>

1080
01:18:17,778 --> 01:18:20,322
<font color="#FFFFFF">Choose someone else.</font>

1081
01:18:21,113 --> 01:18:22,448
<font color="#FFFFFF">Please.</font>

1082
01:18:41,551 --> 01:18:42,802
<font color="#FFFFFF">No.</font>

1083
01:18:58,693 --> 01:19:00,987
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're a long ways
past the reef.</font>

1084
01:19:02,363 --> 01:19:03,364
<font color="#FFFFFF">Gramma?</font>

1085
01:19:05,367 --> 01:19:08,369
<font color="#FFFFFF">Guess I chose the right tattoo.</font>

1086
01:19:08,828 --> 01:19:09,829
<font color="#FFFFFF">Gramma!</font>

1087
01:19:15,460 --> 01:19:17,546
<font color="#FFFFFF">I tried, Gramma.</font>

1088
01:19:19,463 --> 01:19:21,173
<font color="#FFFFFF">I couldn't do it.</font>

1089
01:19:21,925 --> 01:19:24,427
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's not your fault.</font>

1090
01:19:24,594 --> 01:19:28,347
<font color="#FFFFFF">I never should have put so much
on your shoulders.</font>

1091
01:19:29,181 --> 01:19:31,184
<font color="#FFFFFF">If you are ready to go home...</font>

1092
01:19:32,685 --> 01:19:34,688
<font color="#FFFFFF">I will be with you.</font>

1093
01:19:51,246 --> 01:19:52,872
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why do you hesitate?</font>

1094
01:19:54,291 --> 01:19:55,958
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't know.</font>

1095
01:19:59,546 --> 01:20:01,881
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ I know a girl from an island</i></font>

1096
01:20:02,923 --> 01:20:05,594
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ She stands apart from the crowd</i></font>

1097
01:20:06,051 --> 01:20:09,055
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ She loves the sea and her people</i></font>

1098
01:20:09,555 --> 01:20:11,725
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ She makes her whole family proud</i></font>

1099
01:20:12,893 --> 01:20:15,604
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ Sometimes the world
seems against you</i></font>

1100
01:20:16,313 --> 01:20:19,106
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ The journey may leave a scar</i></font>

1101
01:20:19,274 --> 01:20:22,068
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ But scars can heal and reveal just</i></font>

1102
01:20:22,234 --> 01:20:24,820
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ Where you are</i></font>

1103
01:20:25,779 --> 01:20:28,742
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ The people you love will change you</i></font>

1104
01:20:29,117 --> 01:20:31,994
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ The things you have learned
will guide you</i></font>

1105
01:20:32,244 --> 01:20:35,582
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ And nothing on earth can silence</i></font>

1106
01:20:35,748 --> 01:20:38,752
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ The quiet voice still inside you</i></font>

1107
01:20:39,252 --> 01:20:42,421
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ And when that voice starts to whisper</i></font>

1108
01:20:42,588 --> 01:20:45,257
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ Moana, you've come so far</i></font>

1109
01:20:46,009 --> 01:20:47,761
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ Moana, listen</i></font>

1110
01:20:47,927 --> 01:20:52,599
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ Do you know who you are?</i></font>

1111
01:20:54,850 --> 01:20:56,269
<font color="#FFFFFF">Who am I?</font>

1112
01:20:58,313 --> 01:21:01,774
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ I am a girl who loves my island</i></font>

1113
01:21:02,149 --> 01:21:05,737
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ And the girl who loves the sea</i></font>

1114
01:21:06,112 --> 01:21:09,198
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ It calls me</i></font>

1115
01:21:11,283 --> 01:21:14,162
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ I am the daughter of the village chief</i></font>

1116
01:21:14,703 --> 01:21:17,582
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ We are descended from voyagers</i></font>

1117
01:21:17,998 --> 01:21:20,335
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ Who found their way across the world</i></font>

1118
01:21:20,793 --> 01:21:22,753
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ They call me</i></font>

1119
01:21:24,463 --> 01:21:26,966
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ I've delivered us to where we are</i></font>

1120
01:21:27,634 --> 01:21:30,302
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ I have journeyed farther</i></font>

1121
01:21:30,804 --> 01:21:33,180
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ I am everything I've learned and more</i></font>

1122
01:21:33,556 --> 01:21:35,350
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ Still it calls me</i></font>

1123
01:21:37,519 --> 01:21:39,813
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ And the call isn't out there at all</i></font>

1124
01:21:39,979 --> 01:21:42,774
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ It's inside me</i></font>

1125
01:21:43,190 --> 01:21:45,150
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ It's like the tide</i></font>

1126
01:21:45,318 --> 01:21:49,573
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ Always falling and rising</i></font>

1127
01:21:50,030 --> 01:21:52,492
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ I will carry you here in my heart</i></font>

1128
01:21:52,658 --> 01:21:55,703
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ You remind me</i></font>

1129
01:21:55,869 --> 01:21:58,832
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ That come what may</i></font>

1130
01:21:58,998 --> 01:22:02,002
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ I know the way</i></font>

1131
01:22:02,167 --> 01:22:06,756
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ I am Moana</i></font>

1132
01:22:41,207 --> 01:22:43,417
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I am Moana of Motunui</i></font>

1133
01:22:44,877 --> 01:22:45,878
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Aboard my boat...</i></font>

1134
01:22:46,212 --> 01:22:48,381
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I will sail across the sea...</i></font>

1135
01:22:48,756 --> 01:22:51,717
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>and restore the heart of Te Fiti.</i></font>

1136
01:23:27,921 --> 01:23:29,922
<font color="#FFFFFF">Te Kā can't follow us into the water.</font>

1137
01:23:30,756 --> 01:23:32,257
<font color="#FFFFFF">We make it past the barrier islands...</font>

1138
01:23:33,092 --> 01:23:34,260
<font color="#FFFFFF">We make it to Te Fiti.</font>

1139
01:23:34,844 --> 01:23:36,095
<font color="#FFFFFF">None of which you understand...</font>

1140
01:23:36,845 --> 01:23:38,264
<font color="#FFFFFF">because you are a chicken.</font>

1141
01:24:44,872 --> 01:24:45,873
<font color="#FFFFFF">No!</font>

1142
01:24:47,167 --> 01:24:49,586
<font color="#FFFFFF">Heihei! No, no, no!</font>

1143
01:24:51,171 --> 01:24:52,337
<font color="#FFFFFF">Nice work!</font>

1144
01:25:01,722 --> 01:25:02,849
<font color="#FFFFFF">Te Fiti.</font>

1145
01:25:28,207 --> 01:25:29,208
<font color="#FFFFFF">Maui!</font>

1146
01:25:33,880 --> 01:25:34,922
<font color="#FFFFFF">You came back.</font>

1147
01:25:38,760 --> 01:25:40,052
<font color="#FFFFFF">But your hook.</font>

1148
01:25:40,220 --> 01:25:41,720
<font color="#FFFFFF">One more hit and...</font>

1149
01:25:42,596 --> 01:25:44,056
<font color="#FFFFFF">Te Kā's gotta catch me first.</font>

1150
01:25:47,226 --> 01:25:48,269
<font color="#FFFFFF">I got your back, Chosen One.</font>

1151
01:25:49,729 --> 01:25:50,729
<font color="#FFFFFF">Go save the world.</font>

1152
01:25:50,814 --> 01:25:51,814
<font color="#FFFFFF">Maui.</font>

1153
01:25:52,689 --> 01:25:53,733
<font color="#FFFFFF">Thank you.</font>

1154
01:25:54,692 --> 01:25:55,984
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're welcome.</font>

1155
01:26:17,047 --> 01:26:18,173
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hot-hot-hot, hot-hot-hot!</font>

1156
01:26:29,644 --> 01:26:31,104
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey, Te Kā!</font>

1157
01:26:31,854 --> 01:26:32,855
<font color="#FFFFFF">Shark head!</font>

1158
01:26:45,952 --> 01:26:46,953
<font color="#FFFFFF">Moana!</font>

1159
01:26:57,296 --> 01:26:59,172
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get the heart to the spiral!</font>

1160
01:27:37,002 --> 01:27:39,130
<font color="#FFFFFF">Te Fiti...</font>

1161
01:27:39,296 --> 01:27:40,715
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's gone.</font>

1162
01:27:53,353 --> 01:27:55,020
<font color="#FFFFFF">Te Kā!</font>

1163
01:28:30,974 --> 01:28:32,100
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let her come to me.</font>

1164
01:28:55,581 --> 01:28:59,085
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ I have crossed the horizon to find you</i></font>

1165
01:29:06,341 --> 01:29:08,720
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ I know your name</i></font>

1166
01:29:12,515 --> 01:29:16,351
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ They have stolen the
heart from inside you</i></font>

1167
01:29:21,106 --> 01:29:24,193
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ But this does not define you</i></font>

1168
01:29:27,779 --> 01:29:31,783
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ This is not who you are</i></font>

1169
01:29:33,453 --> 01:29:38,707
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ You know who you are</i></font>

1170
01:29:45,547 --> 01:29:48,216
<font color="#FFFFFF">Who you truly are.</font>

1171
01:30:11,323 --> 01:30:12,408
<font color="#FFFFFF">Te Fiti!</font>

1172
01:30:52,989 --> 01:30:54,367
<font color="#FFFFFF">The chicken lives.</font>

1173
01:30:56,202 --> 01:30:58,203
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm sorry about your hook.</font>

1174
01:30:58,703 --> 01:31:01,707
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, hook, no hook...</font>

1175
01:31:02,207 --> 01:31:03,792
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm Maui.</font>

1176
01:31:22,185 --> 01:31:24,479
<font color="#FFFFFF">Te Fiti!</font>

1177
01:31:25,648 --> 01:31:27,483
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey, I mean, how you been?</font>

1178
01:31:30,819 --> 01:31:33,238
<font color="#FFFFFF">Look, what I did was...</font>

1179
01:31:33,405 --> 01:31:34,823
<font color="#FFFFFF">wrong.</font>

1180
01:31:34,990 --> 01:31:37,033
<font color="#FFFFFF">I have no excuse.</font>

1181
01:31:37,659 --> 01:31:38,743
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm sorry.</font>

1182
01:31:47,752 --> 01:31:51,256
<font color="#FFFFFF">You know, it'd be rude to refuse
a gift from a goddess.</font>

1183
01:31:56,095 --> 01:31:57,095
<font color="#FFFFFF">Thank you.</font>

1184
01:31:57,220 --> 01:31:59,765
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your kind gesture is
deeply appreciated.</font>

1185
01:32:49,649 --> 01:32:51,067
<font color="#FFFFFF">Gonna miss you, drumstick.</font>

1186
01:32:51,234 --> 01:32:52,318
<font color="#FFFFFF">You could come with us, you know.</font>

1187
01:32:53,235 --> 01:32:56,822
<font color="#FFFFFF">My people are going to need
a master wayfinder.</font>

1188
01:32:58,323 --> 01:33:00,158
